And this brings us to the point of this review. As we can see from the Advanced LIGO design sensitivity shown in Fig. 1, the fundamental quantum fluctuations of light are limiting the sensitivity of the current generation of GW detectors in the most of its detection band, above ∼\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
