				\begin{document}$$\sim $$\end{document} 10 Hz. The dominant noises below 10 Hz comprise seismic and gravity gradient fluctuations (Harms 2015) together with suspension thermal noise (LIGO Scientific Collaboration 2018), while at medium frequencies around ∼\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
