				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\hat{P} = m\hat{v} - g_{\mathrm{SM}}(t)\hat{a}_c$$\end{document} than a simple proportionality to velocity (see, e.g., Sect. 4.5.2 in Danilishin and Khalili 2012), where gSM(t)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
