				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\lambda /4$$\end{document}-plate, PBS and a mirror for the same purpose (Danilishin et al. 2018)

