Specifically in the context of the large-scale gravitational-wave detectors the optical rigidity was analyzed in Braginsky et al. (1997), Buonanno and Chen (2001), Khalili (2001), Buonanno and Chen (2002), Buonanno and Chen (2003). Most notably, it was shown in these works that in very long cavities with the bandwidth γ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
