				\begin{document}$$\omega _0\pm \varOmega $$\end{document} when propagating inside the arm cavity that is tuned on resonance with respect to the carrier frequency ω0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
